title: Black Ice v0.8.047
description: Black Ice is a Hack and Shoot  a Cyberpunk First-Person Shooter / Hack & Slash RPG about hacking.  Think Borderlands meets Tron.  The cyber-world is huge, the colors are neon, the loot is randomized, and the lasers are loud.  Black Ice is currently in Beta, with updates on the way.FeaturesFast-paced First Person Shooting with a flexible level up and customization system Billions of randomly generated items - Railguns! Rocket shotguns! Disco Deathballs! Seamless 10-player online multiplayer
